{"type":"message","id":"b25ae9ff","parentId":"17fc7a1f","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:58:03.465Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-04-02 23:58 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态，整理3-5条关键信息。每条信息包含：标题、摘要、来源网站、发布时间。输出格式为Markdown。"}],"timestamp":1775145483462}}
{"type":"message","id":"221615c2","parentId":"b25ae9ff","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:58:11.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is to search for industry news related to 道简网络's business (enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, IT operations services) and compile 3-5 key pieces of information in Markdown format with title, summary, source website, and publication date.\n\nLet me use the web search skill to find the latest industry news.","thinkingSignature":"9bbf26ffc09867d2ca84215b1d454b58324dd0f03922eeb530886da129864a39"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_utqlguadw53a_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":113,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42010,"totalTokens":42240,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001356,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.005041199999999999,"total":0.005211899999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775145483464}}
{"type":"message","id":"753b4f20","parentId":"221615c2","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:58:11.616Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_utqlguadw53a_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775145491614}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8d94bd1","parentId":"753b4f20","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:58:16.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me search for the latest industry news related to enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"833a871704cbba6047b2b02dba30cc89f8f32d0d577c3ec3d3db2b213e8117a9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l717bi08xgw8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新动态 政策\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l717bi08xgw8_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 弱电工程 行业动态 2026\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l717bi08xgw8_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 行业趋势 2026\" --output json","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":855,"output":194,"cacheRead":41900,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42949,"cost":{"input":0.0002565,"output":0.0002328,"cacheRead":0.0012569999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017463}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775145491616}}
